    "body": "@bergmeister I agree partially on the first 3 checkboxes and updated the checklist, but just because we can't force people doesn't mean we can't remind them.  As a maintainer, the results are much better with the checklist.\r\n\r\nThe problem with using unchecked as not applicable could mean they haven't gotten around to it or that it's not applicable, but I think I would be ok with it.  I added the maintainers and Steve for additional feedback.",
